WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.790
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:04.630
joining me today. It's just me

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:06.630
today, but I'm excited to be

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:09.030
here, and I pray you are too.

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:12.070
Yesterday, when

00:00:12.070 --> 00:00:12.080
Diana

00:00:12.080 --> 00:00:13.990
and I were praying

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.829
over the things the Lord

00:00:15.839 --> 00:00:18.390
had for us, it was over the top.

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:22.070
The presence of the Lord was tangible in

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:24.390
this house. The Lord showed

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:27.109
me again one last call; His

00:00:27.119 --> 00:00:30.390
eyes were looking over the horizon

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:33.030
at the sheep that were lost.

00:00:34.559 --> 00:00:36.470
He would leave the 99 and go after

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:40.069
the one. I could see Him longing for

00:00:40.079 --> 00:00:43.590
His lost child, the lost ones,

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:46.389
the wayward people in

00:00:46.389 --> 00:00:46.399
the backfields.

00:00:46.399 --> 00:00:49.190
He's coming for you.

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:51.110
I believe

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:52.630
even Braden loved it when the

00:00:52.640 --> 00:00:55.189
Lord said, "The devil came at the

00:00:55.199 --> 00:00:57.029
youth hard, but I'm going to come at

00:00:57.039 --> 00:00:59.750
them harder. I'm coming for the

00:00:59.760 --> 00:01:02.310
youth of this generation."He said, "I'm

00:01:02.320 --> 00:01:05.350
coming back for

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:08.630
a glorious church,"but man, what the

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:11.750
Lord has in store for the youth! I

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:13.510
believe we're about to see some of the

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:16.550
greatest moves of the Spirit of the Lord

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:19.190
we've ever seen

00:01:19.190 --> 00:01:19.200
before—demonstrations

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.830
and manifestations of the glory of God.

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:23.429
I know the Bible says there's a

00:01:23.439 --> 00:01:26.310
great falling away. I understand that,

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:28.550
but I know what He also said to me. He

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:30.710
said, "Brandon, I'm coming for the

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:32.630
one."Do

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:36.069
you realize how much

00:01:36.079 --> 00:01:38.870
Jesus loves you today? Do you realize

00:01:38.880 --> 00:01:41.670
how much He has a plan for your life?

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:44.710
Every single one of you, He loves.

00:01:44.720 --> 00:01:47.590
When we go through a major city

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:50.870
and I see all the people, I think, "Isn't

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:55.190
it amazing that He has interest in every

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:58.469
single one of us?"There are millions and billions of us. There

00:01:58.469 --> 00:01:58.479
are

00:01:58.479 --> 00:02:00.550
only

00:02:00.550 --> 00:02:00.560
300-some

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:02.230
million people in the United States;

00:02:02.240 --> 00:02:04.709
around the world, there

00:02:04.709 --> 00:02:04.719
are

00:02:04.719 --> 00:02:06.789
billions. Think about that.

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:10.710
He has a plan, and He knows every

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:13.190
hair on your head. He knows your

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:16.309
past, He knows your future, and He knows

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:18.630
everything about you. He knows the day

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:21.150
you're going to take your last

00:02:21.160 --> 00:02:23.830
breath, but He wants every one of

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:26.550
you to know Him. That's exciting.

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:27.750
It's

00:02:27.760 --> 00:02:30.070
overwhelming to me to think that He has

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:32.229
a plan for every single one of us and

00:02:32.239 --> 00:02:33.670
that He knows us

00:02:33.670 --> 00:02:33.680
all

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:36.390
that well. He knows all our faults

00:02:36.390 --> 00:02:36.400
and

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:38.790
our pains; He knows what

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:40.309
you're bad at and what you're

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:41.670
good at.

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:44.390
It's amazing. God is a good God. I

00:02:44.400 --> 00:02:45.830
was excited. A lot of people

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:47.750
say, "What does Sooner

00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:47.760
mean?"or

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:49.670
"What did you see,

00:02:49.670 --> 00:02:49.680
Sooner?"I

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:53.550
believe it is a representation of the land

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:56.830
run. If you look at what the

00:02:56.840 --> 00:03:00.390
Sooners do—the same

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:03.110
reason why they named the college the

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.830
Oklahoma

00:03:05.830 --> 00:03:05.840
Sooners—He

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:09.190
highlighted "Sooners"in an

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:12.790
arch before me. He was talking about

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:16.309
Japan and South Korea, and I thought that

00:03:16.319 --> 00:03:18.390
was interesting because He

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:20.470
highlighted that to me. People say,

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:22.309
"How do you see all this? Oh, you just

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:24.149
have a great imagination,

00:03:24.149 --> 00:03:24.159
Brandon."I'm

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:27.350
not that good, I'll

00:03:27.360 --> 00:03:29.430
be real with y'all. If you realized

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:31.190
who is talking to

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:33.430
you behind the camera, you would go, "Wow."Seriously,

00:03:33.430 --> 00:03:33.440
I

00:03:33.440 --> 00:03:36.949
think it's

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:39.270
amazing the things the Lord will

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:42.670
show us in prayer if you seek

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:45.830
Him. When He talked about Iraq again,

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:46.949
people say, "Well, are you talking

00:03:46.959 --> 00:03:49.270
about the revaluation of the Iraqi

00:03:49.270 --> 00:03:49.280
dinar?"I

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:52.550
have no idea. When I'm in

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:54.869
the Spirit like that and saying what

00:03:54.879 --> 00:03:57.910
I'm seeing, I don't remember a lot of

00:03:57.920 --> 00:04:01.429
what I'm saying because I'm

00:04:01.439 --> 00:04:03.589
flowing with the Holy Ghost. So my

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:06.869
son and my wife will say,

00:04:06.879 --> 00:04:08.470
"This is what you said,"because Diana

00:04:08.470 --> 00:04:08.480
or Braden takes

00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:11.030
notes of

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:13.270
everything the Lord shows me

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:15.350
whenever I'm praying; that's what

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:18.789
we do in our private time. We're

00:04:18.799 --> 00:04:21.830
just doing more private time

00:04:21.830 --> 00:04:21.840
in

00:04:21.840 --> 00:04:24.230
public view so people can see

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:26.870
us and how the Lord flows. This is what

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:29.749
we do on a day-to-day basis. This is how

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:32.390
serious we take it. The Holy Spirit

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:34.310
visits us like this all the time.

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:37.189
I'm not bragging; it's just real.

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:39.110
He will

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:41.110
show us that which is to come. This is how

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:44.230
the Trump ear prophecy came out. This is

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:47.350
how saying there would be a red wave

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:51.590
or XRP, and

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:53.430
all these things He's

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:56.310
showing me about wars and

00:04:56.310 --> 00:04:56.320
the plague—it

00:04:56.320 --> 00:04:59.189
is all birthed out of

00:04:59.199 --> 00:05:02.030
prayer. I don't just walk

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:04.629
around and get these prophetic

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:06.870
words. I told you, I don't feel

00:05:06.880 --> 00:05:09.189
like I walk in a prophetic gift; I'm

00:05:09.199 --> 00:05:11.510
a watchman. It's totally different

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:13.430
than somebody who walks around saying, "I

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:15.469
hear the voice of the

00:05:15.469 --> 00:05:15.479
Lord."That's

00:05:15.479 --> 00:05:18.390
amazing when it happens, don't get me

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:21.790
wrong, but I see when I

00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:24.310
pray in the Spirit, not

00:05:24.320 --> 00:05:26.070
in English. Even

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:28.390
my kids say, "Dad prays in tongues and Dad

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:29.830
prays a lot in tongues, and that's what

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:31.670
we do."I get in the car and drive

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:33.510
around, and the Lord shows me things:

00:05:33.520 --> 00:05:35.510
open-eyed visions. I don't close my eyes

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:37.430
when I'm driving around and

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:40.550
run into somebody! I'm praying

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:41.909
and looking, and all of a sudden,

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:43.830
He'll show me an open-eyed vision.

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:45.990
I'll see things, and the Lord will show

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.510
me that which is to come. I believe

00:05:47.520 --> 00:05:50.390
that's a gift. I believe God gives those

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:52.710
gifts to intercessory prayer

00:05:52.710 --> 00:05:52.720
people—people

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:54.550
who intercede for the nations.

00:05:54.550 --> 00:05:54.560
They

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:56.629
intercede and

00:05:56.629 --> 00:05:56.639
are

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:58.550
prayer people. I believe that He's

00:05:58.560 --> 00:06:00.070
no respecter of persons; what He'll

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:02.390
do for me, He'll do for you. I say it

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:04.550
all the time: "Father, give me eyes to

00:06:04.560 --> 00:06:07.430
see what I need to see and ears

00:06:07.430 --> 00:06:07.440
for

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:09.590
what I need to

00:06:09.590 --> 00:06:09.600
hear."I

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:11.830
thank You, Lord, that I am

00:06:11.830 --> 00:06:11.840
never

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:14.150
snared by any satanic or demonic

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:16.870
force. I thank You, Father, that no

00:06:16.880 --> 00:06:18.550
weapon formed against me will prosper,

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:21.350
but I hear Your voice, and a stranger's

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:23.909
voice I will not follow. I hear You,

00:06:23.919 --> 00:06:26.790
Father; You speak to me and

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:29.029
show me that which is to come as I sit

00:06:29.039 --> 00:06:32.070
on the wall. That's what I do.

00:06:32.080 --> 00:06:34.629
I confess that over myself all

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:38.469
the time: I hear and see what the Father

00:06:38.479 --> 00:06:41.350
wants me to see. And I take communion. I

00:06:41.350 --> 00:06:41.360
have

00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:42.870
these communion

00:06:42.870 --> 00:06:42.880
cups—we've

00:06:42.880 --> 00:06:44.710
got communion

00:06:44.720 --> 00:06:46.150
everywhere: the living room,

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:47.590
the kitchen, the

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:49.350
bedrooms.

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:51.749
We have it in the car.

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:55.350
We go before the Lord with communion all

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:57.670
the time. We like it so much, I told y'all

00:06:57.680 --> 00:06:59.870
I'm turning

00:06:59.880 --> 00:07:02.790
purple! It's just funny to us

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:05.309
because we say we're turning

00:07:05.319 --> 00:07:07.830
purple. Billy Burke says that:

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:09.589
"I turn purple, I turn

00:07:09.589 --> 00:07:09.599
purple,"because

00:07:09.599 --> 00:07:12.309
we take communion so much.

00:07:12.319 --> 00:07:15.110
We believe in the

00:07:15.120 --> 00:07:16.710
anointing and the power of

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:19.110
the Holy Spirit. We believe Jesus

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:21.189
Christ has chosen us and we are called to

00:07:21.199 --> 00:07:24.070
the kingdom for such a time as this.

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:25.589
We're excited you're here. We're

00:07:25.599 --> 00:07:28.230
believing for a million-man

00:07:28.230 --> 00:07:28.240
and woman

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:30.629
prayer army to pray on this channel,

00:07:30.629 --> 00:07:30.639
as

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:32.790
He told us. He said, "Brandon, you do

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:35.670
this and we can change the course

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:39.110
of governments and things all around

00:07:39.110 --> 00:07:39.120
us."So

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:41.350
we saw about

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:43.189
that yesterday. We saw the Sooners

00:07:43.189 --> 00:07:43.199
and

00:07:43.199 --> 00:07:45.270
the things we prayed about Iraq. I

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:47.189
told you about the attacks; I said we're

00:07:47.199 --> 00:07:48.909
praying against attacks against our

00:07:48.909 --> 00:07:48.919
bases—our

00:07:48.919 --> 00:07:51.909
army bases and

00:07:51.919 --> 00:07:53.670
naval bases in Iraq.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:55.830
I'm not familiar with them, but I saw

00:07:55.840 --> 00:08:00.629
bases being targets for war.

00:08:00.639 --> 00:08:02.950
So we pray against that and for

00:08:02.950 --> 00:08:02.960
the Houthis,

00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:06.070
that they will not be able to hurt

00:08:06.080 --> 00:08:07.909
any of our service people, that they're

00:08:07.919 --> 00:08:09.670
always in the right place at the right

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:11.270
time, and no weapon formed against them

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:13.909
will prosper. We pray over

00:08:13.919 --> 00:08:16.029
that. I've prayed over

00:08:16.039 --> 00:08:18.670
what the Lord showed me about Kim

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:21.749
Jong-un, the troops going over

00:08:21.759 --> 00:08:24.830
in the train, and the war trying to

00:08:24.840 --> 00:08:27.749
escalate. I see it. Then

00:08:27.759 --> 00:08:29.589
we were praying over... there

00:08:29.599 --> 00:08:31.510
was a lot.

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:33.350
We had our list, but I

00:08:33.360 --> 00:08:35.909
thought, "Well, what's fresh

00:08:35.909 --> 00:08:35.919
today?"If

00:08:35.919 --> 00:08:37.670
the Lord shows us something today, cool.

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:39.709
If he doesn't, I always go with

00:08:39.719 --> 00:08:41.829
anticipation that God is going to show

00:08:41.839 --> 00:08:43.670
up and show off and show us what

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:45.990
he wants us to see. So, we

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:48.389
pray you're excited. We pray

00:08:48.389 --> 00:08:48.399
you

00:08:48.399 --> 00:08:50.150
want to be a part of this. And let's

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:52.389
just get started. So, we always take

00:08:52.399 --> 00:08:54.150
communion to start off. I always enter

00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:55.590
by the blood of the Lamb, by the word of

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:58.710
our testimony.

00:08:58.720 --> 00:09:01.150
Thank you, Father, for all that you've

00:09:01.160 --> 00:09:03.430
done. Thank you, Father, for all that

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:04.870
you've done for us. I thank you, God,

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:07.509
that you set us free by the blood. You

00:09:07.519 --> 00:09:08.710
said you were wounded for our

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:10.070
transgressions. You were bruised for our

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:11.990
iniquities. The chastisement of our

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:14.550
peace was upon you. And with your

00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:16.949
stripes, we are healed. And Father, we

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:18.310
thank you, Lord, for your body that was

00:09:18.320 --> 00:09:20.230
broken for us today. And we take this

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:23.030
body and we thank you, Lord, that by

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:25.509
your stripes, we are healed. And we take

00:09:25.519 --> 00:09:27.590
it right now in the name of Jesus. And

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:29.829
we are healed from the top of our head

00:09:29.839 --> 00:09:32.230
to the soles of our feet. And we're

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:35.590
expecting the manifestation of

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:37.750
what we've been believing for now in

00:09:37.750 --> 00:09:37.760
Jesus'name.

00:09:37.760 --> 00:09:39.829
Father, we thank you, Lord,

00:09:39.839 --> 00:09:41.670
that we're delivered. We're delivered

00:09:41.680 --> 00:09:43.829
from all bondage. We're delivered in

00:09:45.670 --> 00:09:45.680
Jesus'name.

00:09:48.120 --> 00:09:56.310
And we thank you, Father, for it.

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:59.790
Lord, we plead the blood of Jesus over

00:09:59.800 --> 00:10:02.230
us. You said in your word, if

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:04.550
we confess our sin, you're faithful and

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:06.150
just to forgive us of our sin and

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.470
cleanse us from all unrighteousness. And

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:10.389
we plead the blood of Jesus over us

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:13.350
today, God. And we thank you, Lord, for

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:15.670
we make much of the blood, and the blood

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:18.069
will make much of us. And we plead the

00:10:18.079 --> 00:10:20.710
blood of Jesus Christ over us today. And

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:23.590
we thank you, Father, that

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:27.509
it is well with us

00:10:27.519 --> 00:10:30.590
in our soul. And we come up

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:34.630
higher with the fire. And we see from an

00:10:34.640 --> 00:10:35.870
eagle's

00:10:35.880 --> 00:10:39.509
eye, not down on the lower level,

00:10:39.519 --> 00:10:42.069
but Father, we come up higher with you

00:10:42.079 --> 00:10:44.710
on the higher level, seated with you in

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:47.509
the heavenlies. And we take our seat. We

00:10:47.519 --> 00:10:49.670
take our rightful place with you right

00:10:49.680 --> 00:10:51.990
now in the name of Jesus. And we thank

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:53.190
you, Lord, that you're making

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:55.829
intercession for us at the right hand of

00:10:55.839 --> 00:10:58.230
the Father. And we take this blood right

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:00.550
now and we plead the blood of Jesus

00:11:00.560 --> 00:11:03.030
Christ over us. And we thank you,

00:11:03.040 --> 00:11:05.910
Father, that what you bore in your body,

00:11:05.920 --> 00:11:08.310
we don't have to bear in our own. We're

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:10.310
healed and whole and well in the name of

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:12.389
